name: RZ Minjourney (2.1)
description:
A new era for StableDiffusion2, for 41 kb !

This embetting is suitable for everyone, it can help to create logos / t-shirt designs and can act as an helper to clean your scenes.

Here is a supportive edition Minjourney Ext. with cool goodies such as prompts, the new Apex alternative embedding, my dynamic prompts for batch testing and my visionary art'ish cooked prompt, check it out !

Creative illustrations

An house by rzminjourney

A colorful digital illustration by rzminjourney of a cute (chibi) {cat | dog | parrot| girl} wearing { googles | a baseball hat | a headset }, digital painting, artstation, artgerm, great composition, concept art, award winning

A logo design, digital illustration (by rzminjourney) of an ominous alien emerging from deep within the deep space, sci fi, intelligence, technological rings, by gerald brom, trending on artstation, cgsociety

(thoses four pictures was from the same 8-batch output)

A minimalistic digital illustration (by rzminjourney) of a santa in winter, dramatic lighting, colored manga cover, (highly detailed:1.21), trending on artstation, award winning

Plain scenes previews

For full scenes just use your prompts as usual and lower the weights of [rzminjourney] or put the trigger at the end of the prompt

situational negatives :

flowers, ornaments, laurel, baroque = if you want less laurels use that, can improve a too boring typo aswell

A good general negative :

poorly rendered face,poorly drawn face,poor facial details,poorly drawn hands,poorly rendered hands,low resolution.bad composition, mutated body parts,blurry image,disfigured,oversaturated,bad anatomy,deformed body features, drawing, detailed, duplicate, out of frame, nike, uncentered, flowers, ornaments, laurel, baroque

General tips :

Generate on non-squared formats change the overall behaviour of the embedding in a very good way.

Small example of the combination of minjourney and Apex for a very small prompt :
